81b995abb","tid":992024,"uid":23087,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T07:14:43.000Z","msg":"投訴網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/feedback.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcustomer%2Fmain%2Ffeedback.php&d=roOfpUtotHjLxRc6RQnC5JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3f6102e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/customer/main/feedback.php</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tcu.gov.hk/chi/complaint/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tcu.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fcomplaint%2Findex.htm&d=roOfpUtotHjLxRc6RQnC5JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d7321b4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.tcu.gov.hk/chi/complaint/index.htm</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:42:48.000Z","msg":"無用架<br />\n之前環保團體係咁屌佢開冷氣<br />\n地鐵又借名攞正牌咁cut cost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:22:48.000Z","msg":"廷伸閱讀 環保撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府提倡將空調溫度維持於攝氏25.5度，以節省電力，捍衛藍天。但有環保團體跟進多宗冷氣太凍的投訴就發現，多個政府部門和政府作為大股東的港鐵均不能達標，被投訴而又最低溫的港鐵西鐵線，列車車廂溫度僅得攝氏19.8度，較政府倡議的溫度要低近6度，令香港淪為「城市雪房」，出現「穿外套、開冷氣」的怪現象，市民也容易患上「冷氣病」。<br />\n<br />\n實習記者張曉彤、靜態組報道<br />\n<br />\n環保觸覺於去年開設特別投訴網頁，供市民投訴空調過低情況。在本年6月至8月期間，共接獲37宗空調溫度投訴，其中除了冷氣巴及商場外，法庭、酒店會議廳、私家醫院等，而港鐵東涌線更是接獲最多投訴的地方之一。據了解，某些地方的空調溫度較低，是因為該處的通風系統並不完善，為避免遭人投訴悶熱，有關方面只好把空調調低，以減少空氣不流通而做成悶焗，亦有商場因員工的制服過厚，需要調低氣溫以作配合。"},{"pid":"117477e8daca9dca7f494391204abee390a6052b","tid":992024,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T00:44:18.000Z","msg":"狗巴都不惶多讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你明明係有冷氣有抽風架喎<br />\n但一到冬天就死都唔撚開大啲<br />\n一到冬天搭地鐵巴士就焗到頭都暈埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有冇議員反映過"},{"pid":"724c774e22cb5559e6fd11e1d493e582d8dc6d8c","tid":992024,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:22:06.000Z","msg":"日經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f28f230f4e343c82beeff64a0208c17fc982cc1","tid":992024,"uid":125073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c032ebd0694dbe11a21fee89f9809b4cfed466e","tid":992024,"uid":232594,"like":262,"dislike":4,"score":258,"quote":{"pid":"85d30d8784902e395ccd402d021ed41c97c983ff","tid":992024,"uid":78791,"like":34,"dislike":496,"score":-462,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T00:37:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T00:47:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/ch/corporate/images/investor/finhighlight_optprofit_c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fch%2Fcorporate%2Fimages%2Finvestor%2Ffinhighlight_optprofit_c.jpg&h=48a1c314&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每年客運收入成70幾億，即係講緊每日賺緊市民2千幾萬，仲唔夠多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:24:26.000Z","msg":"冇人嫌錢多"},{"pid":"cd8bac1f64a2234830596d4460cd21ea3a9a41cc","tid":992024,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:29:37.000Z","msg":"有無check過，車廂空氣含氧有無15%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dca5e8489a67309fdd5544d412f60f03ba3305","tid":992024,"uid":67485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54466f09f7a2e71c2933c55596aaa6ccab4ab50d","tid":992024,"uid":197337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:16:04.000Z","msg":"巴士直程冇開冷氣,焗到PK,一個人咳就成車攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911d967a0